              <span id="reviewTextContainer2342488979" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16876106128060288329">1992 notebook: sharp little story on taste from an uncompleted collection on the five senses. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

